EchoDEX Voyage Quest - Early supporters

EchoDEX Voyage Quest - Early supporters

EchoDEX Voyage Quest - Early supporters is EchoDEX’s first campaign on Galxe to show appreciation for early supporters. It also serves as a preparation for EchoDEX’s mainnet launch.

By completing these tasks, users not only prove their authenticity but also earn high scores. Additionally, you will contribute to spreading the word about EchoDEX to reach more people. To participate, you must meet at least one of the following conditions:

  • Gitcoin Passport with over 10 points
  • Galxe Passport holders
  • More than 10 transactions on Ethereum

Furthermore, you need to complete additional social tasks to earn more points. We will conduct an airdrop in the near future for those who achieve the required points. Let’s build together!
